OL,3,CUK set to shed 163,000 jobs amid Iran
OL,4,Cwar fallout ` report
OL,6,FOverall it forecasts UK employment
OL,7,Fwill decline by 0.4% this year,
OL,8,Fequivalent to 163,000 job losses on a
OL,9,Fnet basis.
OL,11,FThis will be driven by a pull back in
OL,12,Fconsumer spending, the soaring cost of
OL,13,Ffuel, energy, materials and
OL,14,Fingredients, as well as disruption to
OL,15,Fshipping.
OL,17,FThe Bank of England warned late last
OL,18,Fmonth the rate of UK unemployment
OL,19,Fcould hit 5.6% this year, up from 5.2%
OL,20,Fcurrently, in its more gloomy scenario
OL,21,Ffor the impact of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778461395
OL,3,CUK set to shed 163,000 jobs amid Iran
OL,4,Cwar fallout ` report
OL,6,FThe Item Club said as households rein
OL,7,Fin discretionary spending in the face
OL,8,Fof a surge in the cost of living, the
OL,9,Fretail and hospitality sector will
OL,10,Fsuffer the biggest slowdown across
OL,11,FBritain's major cities.
OL,13,FThe independent forecasting group
OL,14,Fpredicts that employment in London
OL,15,Fwill drop by 25,000 this year as its
OL,16,Fretail and hospitality sector slows,
OL,17,Fwith a 12,500 reduction in Birmingham,
OL,18,F9,800 drop in Leeds and 6,200 decline
OL,19,Fin Glasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778461395
OL,3,CUK set to shed 163,000 jobs amid Iran
OL,4,Cwar fallout ` report
OL,6,FThere may be some bright spots,
OL,7,Fhowever, with Cambridge set to see
OL,8,Femployment growth in 2026, while
OL,9,FBelfast and Edinburgh are expected to
OL,10,Fsee relatively limited job losses.
OL,12,FMr Lyne said: "Across the UK, the jobs
OL,13,Fmarket is going to soften, but it's
OL,14,Flooking especially fragile in South
OL,15,FWales and the Humber as they're
OL,16,Fparticularly exposed to manufacturing
OL,17,Fbusinesses that are seeing big
OL,18,Fincreases in their costs of materials.
OL,26,@tD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778461395
OL,3,CUK set to shed 163,000 jobs amid Iran
OL,4,Cwar fallout ` report
OL,6,F"Resilience will come in places like
OL,7,FCambridge where the tech sector is
OL,8,Fbased."
OL,10,FThe report said that while publicly-
OL,11,Ffunded sectors ` such as education,
OL,12,Fpublic administration and human health
OL,13,Fand social work ` are expected to hire
OL,14,Fmore jobs over the year, this will not
OL,15,Fbe enough to offset wider losses.
OL,17,FIt also warns over a widening gap in
OL,18,Fliving standards across the UK caused
OL,19,Fby the Iran war.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
