OL,3,CUK set to shed 163,000 jobs amid Iran
OL,4,Cwar fallout ` report
OL,6,FLow income areas will see households
OL,7,Fsuffer the steepest hikes in the cost
OL,8,Fof living, as more of their spending
OL,9,Fgoes on essentials, such as food, fuel
OL,10,Fand energy bills, which are set to see
OL,11,Fbig price rises.
OL,13,FHouseholds in cities such as
OL,14,FNewcastle, Belfast and Birmingham
OL,15,Fspend as much as 13% of their
OL,16,Fdisposable income on energy and food,
OL,17,Fcompared to less than 9% for an
OL,18,Faverage household in London, according
OL,19,Fto the report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778461395
OL,3,CUK set to shed 163,000 jobs amid Iran
OL,4,Cwar fallout ` report
OL,6,FThis could see these cities left
OL,7,Fparticularly exposed if the Iran war
OL,8,Fis not resolved soon, the Item Club
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FA Government spokesman said: "Recent
OL,12,Ffigures show that there was an
OL,13,Fimprovement in the labour market at
OL,14,Fthe beginning of the year with
OL,15,Funemployment falling below 5%, and
OL,16,F332,000 more people in work than a
OL,17,Fyear ago.
OL,26,@sD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778461395
OL,3,CUK set to shed 163,000 jobs amid Iran
OL,4,Cwar fallout ` report
OL,6,F"But we cannot escape the effects of
OL,7,Fthe war in the Middle East which are
OL,8,Flikely to feed through to prices and
OL,9,Femployment in the coming months.
OL,11,F"We will do everything we can to
OL,12,Fsupport the country through this
OL,13,Fperiod, including by slashing energy
OL,14,Fbills by up to 25% for 10,000
OL,15,Fmanufacturers.
OL,17,F"Our mission for clean power by 2030
OL,18,Fwill get us off the rollercoaster of
OL,19,Ffossil fuel prices, to cut bills for
OL,20,Fbusinesses and households for good."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@dO]
